Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:13.03,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绽放在书架间的那朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:18.28,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}对我而言可望不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:23.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}字字句句的背后 藏着我的真意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:28.88,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}从来只能憋在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.05,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一旦与周围攀比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.13,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就陷入自我厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}变得畏畏缩缩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:40.18,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却因为你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.56,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}宽下心来
